<p><meta charset="utf-8">Small bites that do the heavy lifting. This is where the crunchy, creamy, salty, and snackable things live&mdash;the sides and appetizers that disappear first and get talked about later. Think classic crowd-pleasers with just enough flair to make them feel intentional, not fussy. </p>


