		</a><!-- .post-thumbnail -->
			<div class="entry-content-wrap">
		<header class="entry-header">

			<div class="entry-taxonomies">
			<span class="category-links term-links category-style-normal">
				<a href="https://brasspine.com/category/einkorn-recipes/" rel="tag">Einkorn Recipes</a> | <a href="https://brasspine.com/category/desserts/" rel="tag">Desserts</a> | <a href="https://brasspine.com/category/side-dishes/" rel="tag">Side Dishes</a>			</span>
		</div><!-- .entry-taxonomies -->
		<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://brasspine.com/cranberry-banana-nut-bread/" rel="bookmark">Easy Homemade Cranberry Banana Nut Bread</a></h3></header><!-- .entry-header -->
	<div class="entry-summary">
		<p>This Cranberry Banana Nut Bread recipe is a delicious twist on my super-moist banana bread, loaded with juicy cranberries and crunchy walnuts for the perfect balance of sweet and tart. Plus, it&rsquo;s a great way to use up any lingering cranberries hiding in your freezer! Instead of regular wheat flour, this recipe uses einkorn wheat&#8230;</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<div class="entry-actions">
		<p class="more-link-wrap">
			<a href="https://brasspine.com/cranberry-banana-nut-bread/" class="post-more-link">
				Read More<span class="screen-reader-text"> Easy Homemade Cranberry Banana Nut Bread</span><span class="kadence-svg-iconset svg-baseline"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="kadence-svg-icon kadence-arrow-right-alt-svg" fill="currentColor" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="27" height="28" viewBox="0 0 27 28"><title>Continue</title><path d="M27 13.953c0 0.141-0.063 0.281-0.156 0.375l-6 5.531c-0.156 0.141-0.359 0.172-0.547 0.094-0.172-0.078-0.297-0.25-0.297-0.453v-3.5h-19.5c-0.281 0-0.5-0.219-0.5-0.5v-3c0-0.281 0.219-0.5 0.5-0.5h19.5v-3.5c0-0.203 0.109-0.375 0.297-0.453s0.391-0.047 0.547 0.078l6 5.469c0.094 0.094 0.156 0.219 0.156 0.359v0z"></path>
