		<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://brasspine.com/sugared-cranberries/" rel="bookmark">Sparkling Sugared Cranberries (3 Ways)</a></h3></header><!-- .entry-header -->
	<div class="entry-summary">
		<p>Some holiday garnishes whisper. Sugared cranberries crackle. Bright, frosty, and unapologetically festive &mdash; they&rsquo;re the little edible jewels that make any dessert, drink, or cheese board suddenly look like it belongs in a vintage holiday magazine. What You Need to Know (Before You Start Coating Things in Sugar) Just sugar, cranberries, and one of three&#8230;</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
