		<aside id="secondary" role="complementary" class="primary-sidebar widget-area sidebar-slug-sidebar-primary sidebar-link-style-normal">
	<div class="sidebar-inner-wrap">
		<section id="media_image-2" class="widget widget_media_image"><img width="683" height="1024" src="https://brasspine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1-min-683x1024.png" class="image wp-image-80479  attachment-large size-large" alt="" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://brasspine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1-min-683x1024.png 683w, https://brasspine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1-min-200x300.png 200w, https://brasspine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1-min-768x1152.png 768w, https://brasspine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1-min.png 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px" /></section><section id="text-4" class="widget widget_text">			<div class="textwidget"><p data-start="87" data-end="338"><strong>I&#8217;m Jessica, nice to meet you!</strong></p>
<p data-start="87" data-end="338">Interior designer by degree, lighting expert by trade, self-taught baker and cocktail creator by obsession. I’m a small-town girl who loves vintage finds, seasonal parties, and food that tastes as good as it looks (or better).</p>
<p data-start="340" data-end="582">At Brass Pine, you’ll find creative cocktails, cozy desserts, and entertaining ideas that make hosting feel fun—not frantic. If you’re into old-school charm, a good Manhattan, and celebrating life’s little moments—you’re in the right place.</p>
</div>
		</section><section id="block-13" class="widget widget_block">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Get in touch!</h2>
